{"id": "1411624909335040072", "channel_id": "1411624909335040072", "type": 0, "author_id": "244028747999608832", "author_name": "vxvendetta", "author_bot": false, "content": "Some units intentions can break or bug the Aigis Petrify status, like Myriam attack after 5 exalts, or Uvhash for the damage threshold (i can't test it right now). \nIs this intetional? it maybe need to be specified in the intention or in the petrify description if that is the case.\nPlus, petrify is removed when a boss is changing phase and becoming immune, but if you use it AFTER the intention changes and the immunity is active, it correctly stop his turn, is this intended too?", "timestamp": "2025-08-31T08:13:25.108000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1411624909578174484", "filename": "imagsscce.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 510863, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411624909335040072/1411624909578174484/imagsscce.png?ex=69ff9565&is=69fe43e5&hm=1f0686ae2543a8f9ed0ce48af7d7f43c7481c7acfae7371ead834e4f6c44bffa&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411624909335040072", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Petrify dispel", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1411659585072398388", "channel_id": "1411659585072398388", "type": 0, "author_id": "244028747999608832", "author_name": "vxvendetta", "author_bot": false, "content": "At the moment this is not a suggestion, but I wanted to have an idea on what the sentiment around Posses is, some seems to don't appreciate the trend of Character Specific Posses, and on my part I can say that I would appreciate if some of the current Posses would be changed to make them more usable, especially considering the new rules introduced in arc2 that demands a bigger investment of keyflare to rouse multiple units.\nSome of the ones that, at least for me, are never used, as a primary in particular, can be the Tulu one, the Wanda one, maybe Clementine one, and some like the Hameln one need too much uses to activate the especial effect.\nWhat is **your opinions** about this topics?", "timestamp": "2025-08-31T10:31:12.448000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-31T10:37:15.734000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Emoji_XLST_O_02", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 3}, {"emoji": "Emoji_AJE_M_04", "emoji_id": "1400771555939844149", "count": 5}], "attachments": [{"id": "1411659585344897135", "filename": "Captuvbcbcre.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 219830, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411659585072398388/1411659585344897135/Captuvbcbcre.JPG?ex=69ff0cf0&is=69fdbb70&hm=77238b749ccef474ce524ccf09c604f5115bd35ed8276429c86e716589bd6b25&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411659585072398388", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "POSSES future and changes", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785"]}
