{"id": "1411718951364202700", "channel_id": "1411718951364202700", "type": 0, "author_id": "532778652337700896", "author_name": "oct3000", "author_bot": false, "content": "https://youtu.be/n86XuBrmPt4?si=vtc8H8UBG8xh92Q2\n有錄影片為證\n\n一啟效果: 基礎防禦在手牌 \"追加一張\" 腺體分裂\n實際效果是 基礎防禦會 \"抽一張\" 腺體分裂\n會影響開局體驗，先打防禦就只會上盾而已。", "timestamp": "2025-08-31T14:27:06.475000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1411718951850873023", "filename": "322870d3e736df4bae178584e05b85d2.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 78203, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411718951364202700/1411718951850873023/322870d3e736df4bae178584e05b85d2.png?ex=69ff443a&is=69fdf2ba&hm=4de5273a5a6a0f813831a204babd295efd7cbea21dfc6daede40be42b22371e5&"}, {"id": "1411718952245002332", "filename": "b72fa5e8c4a1b9b7d7b14f2fc9c53706.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 123973, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411718951364202700/1411718952245002332/b72fa5e8c4a1b9b7d7b14f2fc9c53706.png?ex=69ff443a&is=69fdf2ba&hm=1386509a4f92c838bd793475908c945de53b62663214c4252976753a68a6a9c4&"}], "embeds": [{"type": "video", "title": "aurita_bug", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n86XuBrmPt4", "description": ""}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411718951364202700", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」日服BUG可以在這底回報嗎", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1411603734978625536", "channel_id": "1411603734978625536", "type": 0, "author_id": "244028747999608832", "author_name": "vxvendetta", "author_bot": false, "content": "The description of the PARADOX covenant make you believe that even if the aliemus cap is now 120, the exalt cost is still 100, so, in theory, after exalting you should still have 20 aliemus. But in reality, when you exalt you use all the aliemus and remain at 0.\nIs this a bug or intended? \nCan the description be adjusted to reflect the actual functionality?", "timestamp": "2025-08-31T06:49:16.748000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-31T06:49:35.406000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1411603735515238500", "filename": "aawds.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 29245, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411603734978625536/1411603735515238500/aawds.JPG?ex=69ff81ac&is=69fe302c&hm=469b32a3fbe294c3fed1df095c7cdfd9d17e9c8366c6ff72ebef65d8921f790b&"}, {"id": "1411603735897182229", "filename": "Captuasdfsdfre.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 28550, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1411603734978625536/1411603735897182229/Captuasdfsdfre.JPG?ex=69ff81ac&is=69fe302c&hm=fe63c1ed3c0d56001acb9d538accb23f0fa7624385040937a0d107da2472c559&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411603734978625536", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」PARADOX mistranslation \\bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1411811415936991313", "channel_id": "1411811415936991313", "type": 0, "author_id": "478214049033879563", "author_name": "yannic2112", "author_bot": false, "content": "I suggest adding a testing stage where you can test your units. For example if I have 2 wheels and wonder which is better for a unit, then I could just go to that stage and test it out. This means that you would be able to choose freely on how many units you field (1-4). Additionally, if there would be enough resources from the dev team, maybe also let us choose what level the opponents are on and which opponents we are up agains. But for now, just a general stage for testing would be nice.", "timestamp": "2025-08-31T20:34:31.747000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1411811415936991313", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Testing stage", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
